  "Description": {
    "English": "The <span class=\"name name-technology\">Seed</span> is an echo of life, the last reverberations of a living being.<br><br>This sentience was fused with a lattice of <span class=\"name name-special\">Atlantideum</span>, as though it had germinated together with the crystal.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">种子</span>是生命的回音，象征着一个鲜活的生命最后的反响。<br><br>这个智慧生命已经与一层<span class=\"name name-special\">亚特拉迪姆</span>融为一体，就像是它与水晶一同发芽成长一般。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">種子</span>是生命的回音，是生命體最後的回響。<br><br>此智慧生物已與<span class=\"name name-special\">亞特蘭提德鋼</span>晶格結合，彷彿伴隨著晶體一同成長。"
  },
