  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "On <span class=\"name name-special\">dissonant</span> worlds, use the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Analysis Visor</span> (<span class=\"name name-img\">AIM</span>) to locate <span class=\"name name-special\">Sentience Echoes</span>.<br>At an echo site, deploy a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Scan Harmonizer</span> or <span class=\"name name-technology\">Polyphonic Core</span> with <span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "在<span class=\"name name-special\">不谐世界</span>上时，使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>（<span class=\"name name-img\">AIM</span>）定位<span class=\"name name-special\">智慧回音</span>。<br>在一处回音地点使用<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>部署<span class=\"name name-technology\">扫描和谐器</span>或者<span class=\"name name-technology\">复调核心</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "在<span class=\"name name-special\">不和諧</span>世界，使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析護目鏡</span> (<span class=\"name name-img\">AIM</span>) 找到<span class=\"name name-special\">智慧生物回音</span>。<br>位於回音地點時，使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span> 部署<span class=\"name name-technology\">掃描協和器</span>或<span class=\"name name-technology\">複音核心</span>。"
  },
